<p><strong>Drum glides and felt drum seal</strong> — plastic glide strips and a felt seal that run along the front bulkhead. Part number 4036EL2004A covers the felt seal on most DLGX models. When the felt wears through or the glides crack, you get a scraping or dragging sound that people mistake for bearing failure.</p>

